commit.message: Trim the appveyor envs some more (bundle up by python).
Trim envs to 72. Update some deeps.
Try to fix some Appveyor issues.
Fix some assertions and fix clonefunc for python3.8.
add PYTEST_DONT_REWRITE in order to suppress already imported warning
Don't run cprofile if benchmark ain't enabled. Unfortunatelly it needs more changes to display cprofile without any bench data (they all go through the same data structure - Stats).
Reduce envs on appveyor - they take too long.
Increase minimum requirements. The plugin is broken on older pytest. Closes #142.
